---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="How paw and sage is supported.">
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container-narrow prose">
      <p>
        paw and sage participates in affiliate programs, including the Amazon Associates Program and the Chewy Affiliate Program, and may also participate in other affiliate networks.
      </p>

      <h2>What this means</h2>
      <p>
        When you click on certain product links on this site and make a purchase, paw and sage may earn a small commission at no additional cost to you. These commissions help fund the time spent researching, writing, and maintaining the content on this site.
      </p>

      <h2>How we recommend products</h2>
      <p>
        We only recommend products we would use ourselves or have researched in depth. Editorial recommendations are made independently of any affiliate relationship — meaning we never feature a product solely because of commission rates, and we will sometimes recommend products that pay us nothing if they are the right fit.
      </p>

      <h2>Specific programs</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Amazon Associates:</strong> As an Amazon Associate, paw and sage earns from qualifying purchases.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Chewy Affiliate Program:</strong> paw and sage participates in Chewy's affiliate program through Impact, earning commissions on qualifying purchases.
      </p>

      <h2>Your choices</h2>
      <p>
        You are never obligated to use the affiliate links on this site. You can search for any recommended product directly on the retailer's website. Either way, the recommendation stands.
      </p>

      <p class="updated">
        Last updated: April 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header { padding: 5rem 0 2rem; text-align: center; }
  .page-header .eyebrow { display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .content-section { padding: 2rem 0 5rem; }
  .prose { font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.75; }
  .updated {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-style: italic;
  }
</style>
